exceptions.tactic: unfold Included in |- *; intros F G H; unfold FamilyIntersection in |- *.
exceptions.exn: Cannot coerce FamilyIntersection to an evaluable reference.

exceptions.tactic: intros A H0 x H1; unfold Intersection in H1; apply H1.
exceptions.exn: Cannot coerce Intersection to an evaluable reference.

exceptions.tactic: intros G0 H2; elim H0; [ intro H3; rewrite <- H3; auto with sets | intro H3; auto with sets | idtac ].

original: unfold Included in |- *; intros F G H; unfold FamilyIntersection in |- *. intros A H0 x H1; unfold Intersection in H1; apply H1. intros G0 H2; elim H0; [ intro H3; rewrite <- H3; auto with sets | intro H3; auto with sets | idtac ].
